Package edu.citadel.cprl

Enum Symbol

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<Symbol>
edu.citadel.cprl.Symbol
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<Symbol>, java.lang.constant.Constable
public enum Symbol
extends java.lang.Enum<Symbol>
This class encapsulates the symbols (also known as token types) of the programming language CPRL.
